Subject: FEATURE: min/max values in movie view
Date: Thu, 13 Jan 2011 10:09:50 -0700
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

Add a radio button for determining min/max.  Options are:

User-defined
Local
Global

In the case of local, derive min/max at playback time from the min/max  
for the species in the simulation file.
In the case of global, derive min/max at playback time from the min/ 
max over all species in the simulation file.

When you select local/global, the min/max fill in with the values from  
the selected simulation file, but they will not be stored when the  
window is closed since they are computed at playback.

